    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of an order of containing various species of insects known for their extremely short adult life spans, ranging from 30 minutes to one day, and emergence in large numbers in the summer months.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
